INSTRUCTIONS — AURANT ACEX TRADING SYSTEM
1. OVERVIEW

AURANT ACEX is a multimodal quantitative trading system combining Temporal Fusion Transformers (TFT), time-series Mixture-of-Experts (MoE), and multimodal feature embeddings. The system is designed for financial time-series forecasting, regime adaptation, and backtesting using structured market data stored in compressed Parquet format.

Core capabilities:

Multi-horizon price prediction
Regime-aware trading via MoE routing
Multimodal feature fusion (price, indicators, macro signals)
Scalable dataset pipeline using Parquet
Backtesting with risk-adjusted performance metrics
