3. DATASET DOWNLOAD (KAGGLE)

Dataset link:
https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/adityaravojha/aurant-aseries/data

Step 1: Install Kaggle CLI

pip install kaggle

Step 2: Create API Key
Go to Kaggle account settings
Navigate to API section
Click “Create New API Token”
Download kaggle.json
Step 3: Place API Key

Mac/Linux:

mkdir -p ~/.kaggle
mv kaggle.json ~/.kaggle/
chmod 600 ~/.kaggle/kaggle.json

Windows:

Place file in:
C:\Users<USERNAME>.kaggle\kaggle.json

Step 4: Download dataset

kaggle datasets download -d adityaravojha/aurant-aseries --unzip

4. DATA STRUCTURE

