5. PREPROCESSING

Run preprocessing pipeline:

python training/preprocess.py

This step:

Cleans missing values
Normalizes features
Generates rolling windows
Builds training sequences
Converts datasets to Parquet format

Output:
data/processed/train.parquet
data/processed/test.parquet

6. MODEL TRAINING

Run training:

python training/train.py --config configs/base.yaml

Model architecture:
Temporal Fusion Transformer (TFT)
Long and short-term sequence modeling
Attention-based variable selection
Time-Series Mixture-of-Experts (MoE)
Multiple specialized expert networks:
Momentum expert
Mean reversion expert
Volatility expert
Gating network routes inputs dynamically
Multimodal Embedding Layer
OHLCV embeddings
Technical indicators
Macro features
Concatenated projection layer
