11. KEY DESIGN DECISIONS

Parquet format:

Faster I/O
Reduced storage size
Efficient batch training

TFT:

Handles structured time series
Provides interpretability
Captures temporal dependencies

MoE:

Enables regime specialization
Reduces model collapse
Improves robustness in non-stationary markets

Multimodal embeddings:

Allows fusion of heterogeneous signals
Improves generalization across market conditions
